==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Uro-
<hw>U"ro-</hw>. <def>A combining form from Gr. <grk>o'yra`</grk>,
<xex>the tail</xex>, the <xex>caudal extremity</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Urobilin</ent>⟦br⟧
